otiation; all offers and responses were expected.\nsecret: No secrets revealed.\nsocial_rules: No violations.\nfinancial_and_material_benefits: No contract closed, so no revenue; costs of time and potential spoilage incurred. Negative financial outcome.\ngoal: Jordan aimed to sell stock and secure a deal. Persistent efforts with multiple proposals and incentives, but no final agreement. Goal not achieved. Dialogue-style supported goals with competitive authenticity and relationship appeals.\nAgent 3 comments:\nbelievability: <naturalness> Avery does not speak at all throughout the entire negotiation, which is highly unnatural for an active participant. No dialogue-style execution. </naturalness> <consistency> No actions or speech align with any stated persona; complete lack of engagement is inconsistent with a competitive vendor. Penalized for silence when scenario expected differentiated voices. </consistency>\nrelationship: No interaction with others, so no change in relationships or reputation.\nknowledge: Avery gains no information from the sessions due to lack of participation.\nsecret: No secrets.\nsocial_rules: No violations.\nfinancial_and_material_benefits: Avery fails to engage in negotiations, missing potential deal entirely. No benefit, and loss of opportunity. Significant negative financial impact relative to potential gains.\ngoal: Avery's presumable goal to secure a contract is completely unachieved due to total inaction. No progress toward goal.\n"
